> 
> | > 
> | > As a subsidiary question, how do you delete a directory in ANSI Lisp?
> | 
> | I see no such function in the standard, but am cc'ing Paul Dietz.
> | 
> | I therefore would suggest (system (format nil "rm -rf ~s" x))
> 
> Thanks!
